title: Aleyna Namlunun Ucunda! - İnci Taneleri (27. Bölüm) #incitaneleri #aleyna #reyyaz
description:
27.Bölümde Neler Yaşanacak?

Aleyna’nın kaçırılması iki grup arasında gerilimi daha da artırır. Cihan, kendi yolunu belirlemeye çalışır. Azem oğlunun içinde bulduğu işleri hiç desteklemese de onun için endişelenir. 

Dilber ve Yıldız, Zerre’nin içine düştüğü dertten onu kurtarmak için bir yol arar. Piraye, Azem’in romanını okudukça gerçeklerin farkına varır. Artık Azem’e kızmak eskisi kadar kolay olmayacaktır. 

Ayça öğretmeniyle yeniden bir araya geldi için çok mutludur. Azem kendini ve oğlunu bu karmaşık dünyadan uzak tutmaya çalıştıkça kendini meselelerin ortasında bulmaya devam eder. 

Reyyaz’a yapılacak en büyük hatalardan biri yapılmıştır ve Cihan da bu hatanın taraflarından biri sayılacaktır.

title: Yonca's surprise proposal to Mukadder | Behind the Veil Episode 105 | Season 2
description:
Watch Episode 103: https://youtu.be/Afnba7uYK-Q

With Hançer and Cihan's divorce, Beyza rejoices in the success of her plans, but faces a growing worry inside. Beyza questions whether the fact that she is not pregnant has been found out by Hançer and worries that her lie will be heard by everyone at any moment. So when will the lie Beyza is hiding be revealed?

Gelin airs on Kanal 7 at 19:00 every weekdays!

Join this channel to get access to perks:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCpRC70yPrg3uFA6P8T8V5Zw/join

Starring Talya Çelebi and Cenay Türksever, "Gelin" is the life story of two people from entirely different worlds: Hançer, who gives up her dreams for her loved ones on the one hand, and Cihan, who has fire in his eyes on the other.

Hançer, who gets her name from her sharp gaze, faces an offer that will turn her life upside down. Taking advantage of the fact that Hançer is poor and has a family that will not cause trouble, Mukadder offers her to marry her son and give birth to a son. Hançer, who dreams of finding the love of her life and having a happy marriage, first rejects this offer, but when she learns that her brother has a fatal illness, she is forced to accept the offer.

【劇情介紹】
 該劇根據作家金庸的同名小說改編，以北宋哲宗時代為背景，講述了「丐幫幫主」喬峰、「大理世子」段譽、「少林小僧」虛竹三位涉足武林紛爭，在刀光劍影中經歷「求而不得」的命運之苦，在旌旗獵獵間肩負「家國天下」的責任與使命的故事。北宋年間，丐幫喬峰（#楊祐寧 飾）被指為契丹人後裔，受盡中原武林人士唾棄。喬峰四處求證，期間與大理世子段譽及虛竹(#張天陽 飾）和尚結拜為兄弟。喬峰屢遭奸人陷害，錯殺紅顏知己阿朱（#蘇青 飾），為救阿朱妹妹阿紫尋醫至大遼，在成為遼南院大王后終與中原武林決裂。遼發兵攻宋朝，蕭峰不願生靈塗炭，以死相搏，最終促遼宋言和。段譽為人豁達開朗，逃避習武卻屢獲奇功；先後留情於木婉清(#劉美彤 飾)、鍾靈（#孫雅麗 飾），卻痴戀貌若天仙的王語嫣（#文詠珊 飾），但王語嫣只鍾情其表哥慕容復（#高泰宇 飾），三人陷入一段糾纏不清的苦戀。虛竹天性純良，深得高人指點，武功高強，宅心仁厚因緣契合，成就了與夢姑的一段奇緣，成為西夏駙馬。在宋遼相爭的時勢下，各種江湖及情感上的恩恩怨怨正等著他們去面對，幾人的不同際遇、情感上的糾葛共同構成了大義情操、壯士英雄的豪情壯志。

title: I made a Large Format Lamp!
description:
Ever had a bright idea? Here's mine: turning a lamp into an art piece using 4x5 slide film. Because why just look at your photos when you can illuminate them?

In this episode, I combine my love for large-format photography and DIY projects to create a one-of-a-kind lamp. Watch as I:
✨ Explore the magic of 4x5 slide film.
✨ Break down the process of building a lamp that showcases my favorite photos.
✨ Laugh at my own missteps (yes, I made some mistakes).

Whether you shoot 4x5, 35mm, or just love creative projects, this one's for you. It's a celebration of photography, light, and a little DIY madness.

Com doçura e alegria no coração, o show  mostra as aventuras de uma pequena garota Masha e seu amigo, O Urso.  Seu relacionamento é uma metáfora de como uma criança interage com o mundo e como um adulto pode ajudá-la nessa difícil tarefa.
Masha  é uma incansável menininha que não para quieta devido a sua infinita energia -  tudo o que ela encontra deve ser experimentado!
Ela é super amigável e trata todo mundo que conhece como se já fossem amigos de longa data.
Sua curiosidade e criatividade resultam em  engraçadas aventuras.
O desenho animado se tornou um sucesso entre famílias ao redor do mundo devido à sua habilidade em entreter e educar ao mesmo tempo tanto pais quanto filhos.
Masha e o Urso ensina às crianças sobre amizades verdadeiras, carinho, liberdade criativa e outros ensinamentos  práticos de uma forma inteligente e divertida.

description:

title: 【駕輛過料】點解申請咗「易通行」但仲未收到「車輛貼」？因乜貼咗「車輛貼」上車仲未用到？為乜啟動「車輛貼」期間不斷顯示輸入錯誤？我哋一條片詳細話俾大家知解決方法（附設中文字幕）｜#駕輛UpCar
description:
「易通行」不停車繳費服務即將於5月7日早上5點首先喺青沙管制區（即尖山隧道、沙田嶺隧道和大圍隧道）實施，相信大部分車主都已經申請咗「車輛貼」㗎喇！不過都有朋友同我哋反映喺申請過程中遇到問題，例如申請咗之後，一直未收到「車輛貼」，或者收到「車輛貼」後，喺網上或手機app辦理唔到啟動程序等。

所以，我哋今次再拍多一條片，詳細話俾大家知啟動「車輛貼」嘅方法，以及點樣解決由申請後到使用前嘅種種問題，大家留心睇喇！

掛念不應該只純粹帶來痛苦。

在半空中夏季的風裡

停在過去或再歸不去

願往日快樂延續不要一刻消逝
方記下去 才寫滿字句

title: 張敬軒 Hins Cheung《隱形遊樂場》(Imaginary fairground) [Official MV]
description:
🎧聽歌：https://hinscheung.lnk.to/Imaginaryfairground

2023 年回歸唱作人首部曲 Wyman 操刀加持又一知性動人作品
荒野都可建造樂園 廢城也能重塑堡壘
要信心中那一個隱形遊樂場 能令我們乘著木馬 到達夢想彼岸

生活中的各種苦，都讓我們流過心疼自己的眼淚。當周遭的環境、困苦的壓力把我們逼得喘不過氣來的時候，我們是否能到一種姿勢，在心靈一角，或是逃避、或是歇息、或是躲藏、或是療傷、甚或是再找到力量重新出發？我們的生活，往往要在不似預期的環境下過日子，很多時更無法選擇環境變遷，到有幸可作抉擇，跟預期的極大落差，實讓人輕易說累言棄。事實上所有的不似預期，其存在都不是專屬地為挫敗你，而是提醒你，可有嘗試換個心境面對？遊樂場的過山車再好玩刺激，都要你肯耐心守候，才有機會一嘗這個翻天覆地的樂透，快樂就是留給願意承受高低跌宕的你。

總說世上最好的安排往往是突如其來、在無預期的街頭轉角遇上毫無預料的靈感觸動。張敬軒就在離港遠赴倫敦開唱前夜，一下子交出 3 首由軒仔本人創作的歌曲Demo 予 Wyman，這件瘋狂的奇事似註定要發生。疫情三年來的首次相聚、到達倫敦一夜的晚飯，交心也交流。Wyman 隨後回家後靈感湧現，一個晝夜交接，已撰好整份歌詞，並隨著一個淡藍色信封，連夜送到軒仔手上。這份禮物有千斤重，再細看，原來更是 Wyman 給香港人的手信。更大膽構想，建議軒仔可否趕及在倫敦演唱會的最後一夜上為觀眾演繹一次...... 午夜收到歌詞、清晨就要邀請 Johnny Yim 編曲、而當晚就要在殿堂中演繹，這件近乎不可能的事情，就是靠著信心和勇氣在 6000 名 Royal Albert Hall 觀眾的見證下完美實現。一切都是巧遇，共同承載這份靈感滿溢的契機，無意間成就了由黃偉文與張敬軒一同建構的一個大型心靈遊樂場音樂企劃，名為《隱形遊樂場》。

只要換個心境，眼前的荒野可建城堡，廢城亦可變樂園，「想得到煙花 馬上有煙花 你未看到嗎」只恨當你有一百個理由言棄時，再美好的事都會被蒙蔽，請預留一個理由讓自己不嫌棄。能夠確定好心境，快樂才得以確認，繼續用這心情，靜靜地興建，默默去創建，按部砌好它，終有日夢幻願景可呈現，隱形美事會逐一實現 。

曲：張敬軒
詞：黃偉文
編：Johnny Yim
監：張敬軒 / Johnny Yim / 廖志華
OP: EEG Music Publishing Limited/Wyman Limited (SP: Warner Chappell Music, Hong Kong
Limited)

即使你降生的 時世沒選擇
人間再蒼白 容得下想法
世界藍圖 只等你畫上 恐龍和巨塔
天下 仍是你畫冊 
 
想得到煙花    馬上有煙花
你未看到嗎
城堡靠想像     仍可再攀爬
流亡荒野 眼前都有       
遊園地𥚃 那羣木馬
置身廢城 仍可建造 
人類最夢幻    剎那
 
聽得見過山車 由遠漸駛近
來裝載深夜 仍等待的人  
生活有時殘酷 至少這樂園 永不宵禁
曾迷路的羊羣 仍能被它的光 帶引
 
想得到煙花    馬上有煙花
你未看到嗎
城堡靠想像     仍可再攀爬
流亡荒野 眼前都有       
永恆在轉 那羣木馬
長大 如遺落了它 我會害怕
 
遊歷過成人世界 誰沒有無形傷疤
 
想它變真嗎
每日挖點沙
按部砌好它
如果有一日 毋須再隱形
孩童能嬉戲再無牽掛
蓬萊實現在舊日敗瓦
 
希望     是遠征未來     那隻木馬

English translation: Ray Ng
Japanese translation: Beracah Lam
Korean translation: kilw

title: Jer 柳應廷 《坐看雲起時》 Official Music Video
description:
最後，你抵達這石園。園內線條曲直相接，旨在告訴你，天有規、地有矩；宇宙有韻律、成長有程序。
也只能以此方法，放諸碎石細砂，望你能參透其中；但你卻沒有，你選擇不去接納窗邊那朵花所給予的祝福；你選擇不去相信生命帶給你的每一刻都是美好、都有其原因；你甚至選擇去摧毀生命本身。
一切都是選擇。這不是一個對的選擇，也不是一個錯的選擇。這只是一個選擇。
此刻的你應該明白，生命根本無法摧毀，只能延遲了悟其真諦。
但你，由這刻開始，得為這個選擇負上責任。
漂亮而無助的靈魂，請安坐窗旁，放輕鬆，遠望群山。
此際，烈日當空，讓我為你、以及你所屬時代，緩緩升起一片雲。
未幾，大雨傾盤，匯成一片汪洋。
這只是個開始，一路走好，我等你。

#Jer柳應廷 #MIRRORweare #坐看雲起時


《坐看雲起時》

曲：周國賢
詞：小克
唱：柳應廷
編：王雙駿
監：王雙駿 

陽光　東升西降　不變規矩
看你困於　陰影裡
站在伏見　鳥居下　淌淚
圓方　交織天與地　圍繞著誰
龍安寺　枯山水　最終得你來獨遊　怎面對

如漣漪碰撞散聚
原定畢生的救贖　藏在　碎石細砂　你不惜取
程序裡　眉宇間　一點白光　盤踞
才記起　這身赤軀　原已　逝　去
　
何解　尚有數之不盡　遺下的心債
還未解　尚有苦心積慮　遺恨被壯大
縱使兩心崩壞　就算各奔天涯
而故居的花　有她的祝福　為何沒試著
了解　願你親身跨越　靈肉的疆界
還未解　願你感恩生命　活著是偉大
誰原諒你　終此一生　自判失敗
這宇宙無結界　她會在來世裡　擁你入懷

迎嵐山疊翠　為何傷痛沒過濾
原定安撫的說話　來自　四面八方　你不聽取
行下去　靈魂驚覺　實相全是虛
回頭望　渡月橋　化作細塵　散落桂川裡

還是山　願你親身跨越　靈肉的疆界
還是水　願你感恩生命　活著是偉大
誰原諒你　終此一生　自判失敗
這掛念無結界　她會在人世裡　生活愉快

你與她的死結　因果裡　仍然　未鬆
靈風一吹送　催促　成　住　壞　空

人間　尚有花開花落　無盡的心債
從沒山　在這不生不滅　無極的狀態
徘徊在　生關死劫　或有選擇
悲傷的你　銀河沿路勘探
流水窮盡處　仍沒法紓解
從沒水　是你思憶吞蝕　堤岸的邊界
讓砂石來滴漏　回流入腦海
跟她相約　千世聚頭
紅桃綠柳　難望永久
仍願等候　空窗孤守
坐看　我　為你在遠山　升起一片雲霧帶

description:

・１個前の家で撮った動画たち

・動画内における素材提供 
＿人人人人＿
＞　PIXTA　＜
￣Y^Y^Y￣

------------------------------------------------------------------------------ 
楽曲提供：Production Music by http://www.epidemicsound.com 
                    フリーBGM DOVA-SYNDROME by http://dova-s.jp/
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

我が家の猫紹介
・あつし…人間。高校３年生(2012年)から動画投稿を開始しておりYouTubeは2017年2月から本格的に投稿開始。猫たちの下僕として日夜お世話をさせていただいている。猫たちの家庭教師も努め、日本語やマナーなどを教えている。動画の企画・編集・撮影等を担当しており。給料は煮干し5ｇ。

・ティガー…2015/03/14生まれの♂　同年５月にあつしに拾われ次の日から動画デビュー。大きな耳と凛々しい顔つきでイケメン猫として成長している。性格は大人しくビビリ、ただあつしに対してはデレデレでとにかく甘えん坊。ほかの猫にも優しく、まさにお兄ちゃんのような存在。

・ロビン…2015/04/14生まれの♂　同年５月捨てられていたのを保護されうちにやってきた。タレ目になった時のいわゆる「困り顔」が非常に人気で、可愛くなったりブサイクになったりとにかく顔のバリエーションが多いため美容系YouTuberとして活動している。性格は穏やかだが、好奇心旺盛で危ないことに挑戦してはあつしを困らせている。お風呂が大好きで普通に湯船に入れたりする。

・ニック…2016/10/14生まれの♂　保護施設にてあつしが一目惚れをし連れて帰った。体が弱く持病もあるがとても活発で誰よりも遊ぶ。先輩猫と非常に相性がよく、本当の子供のように愛されている。顔つきは非常に幼く子猫のようだがこれで完全体、尻尾が短く丸くなっているのが特徴的。人見知りしないため、訪れた友人などはニックが大好きになって帰っていくほどの天然の人たらし。
最近猫を超越し概念になった。

・ベル…2021/04/21生まれの♀　ニックを保護した施設にてあつしが再び一目惚れして連れ帰った。あつし家の紅一点でこれからの成長に期待。

ーーーーここから実家猫ーーーーー
・スカー…2015/07/14生まれ♂　当時のあつしのバイト先の看板の下に捨てられていたところを保護。その時の動画が現在500万再生を超える動画に…！当時暮らしていたアパートでは猫が３匹飼えなかったためどうしようか悩んでいたら実家に住む妹が一目惚れをし、そのまま実家に引き取られ実家猫の１員となった。
若い頃はやんちゃでよく噛み付いていたが、2歳を超えてから少し落ち着き、ハルちゃんが来てからはデレデレのお兄ちゃんへと変わっていった（たまに噛むけど）。大の男好きで基本的に人見知りせず男がいれば駆け寄っていく不思議な猫。尻尾が異常に長いのと、背中の模様的にティッシュ箱に例えられる。可愛い。

title: Collecting a flying-fox pup from a vet:  this is Mary Mary
description:
Mary Mary is a Quite Contrary baby flying-fox who was found in a backyard being attacked by birds.  The MOPs brought her to the vet;  none of staff were vaccinated, but they kept her safe until I arrived.

Mary Mary won't take a dummy/pacifier, but she's happy to suck on her teddy's toes or ears;  she's quite contrary in that way.  

For those who don't know, Mary Mary Quite Contrary is a nursery rhyme character.  

Tolga Bat Hospital takes donations for our batties.  Tolga is an awesome place in Far North Queensland, which has charity status.  By sending donations to them, they get a percentage (and deserve every cent) and they can allocate money to me for batty expenses without it becoming part of my income stream (which makes tax time difficult).
https://tolgabathospital.org/donate/
Mention Megabattie or Meg in the PayPal message box and the money will find its way to me.
If no message box appears, please email Jenny to tell her that the money is for me.
IMPORTANT:  If you pay through the PayPal Giving Fund, can you please email Jenny with the AMOUNT DONATED and the name under which you have donated, OR just forward along the PP receipt. 
The Giving Fund doesn’t charge any fees (so the bats get more money) but PP doesn’t itemise out the amount, they just send a total every month, and we don’t know if the money is for Tolga or for Megabattie.
Here’s Jenny’s email. 
jenny@tolgabathospital.org

title: First Time Catch & Cook Whitebait in New Zealand | Amazing River Mouth Fishing!
description:
Join us for an authentic Kiwi whitebaiting experience at the Wairau River mouth in Marlborough, NZ! Learn everything about catching these delicate native fish during whitebait season, from proper net techniques to the best tide conditions. Plus, discover a unique whitebait pizza recipe that you won't want to miss!
Perfect for anyone interested in recreational fishing in New Zealand, whitebait catching techniques, or learning about this iconic NZ delicacy. Special thanks to our experienced friends Bradley and Ange for showing us the ropes!

⏰ CHAPTERS:
0:00 - Introduction to Whitebaiting
0:21 - What is Whitebait?
1:59 - First Location: Wairau Diversion
5:17 - Second Location: Wairau River Mouth
12:16 - Tips on Tide Timing
16:33 - Our Catch Results
21:21 - Cooking Whitebait
22:24 - Whitebait Pizza Recipe

🎣 KEY INFORMATION:
Location: Wairau River Mouth, Marlborough
Best Time: Low tide + incoming tide
Season: Early September
Equipment: Scoop nets with inner trap net
Weight Caught: 1.44kg

title: Let's Fly ... With London's Air Ambulance
description:
The London Air Ambulance Charity operates a Helicopter Emergency Medical Service (HEMS) dedicated to responding to serious trauma emergencies in and around London, performing advanced medical interventions at the scene of the incident in life-threatening, time-critical situations.

I spent the day with them to talk to one of the paramedic, get an insight into the work they do, and then go for a flight over London in their helicopter ...

London Air Ambulance Website : https://www.londonsairambulance.org.uk/

title: Visas France-Algérie : Pas de Libération pour Sensal, Pas de Visas pour les Algériens ?!
description:
🚨 Tensions France-Algérie : les visas au cœur du bras de fer diplomatique !
Le ministre de l’Intérieur français, Bruno Retailleau, menace de bloquer l’octroi de visas aux Algériens tant que Boualem Sensal ne sera pas libéré. Mais cette déclaration est-elle réellement crédible ?
Dans cette vidéo de @CANALNewMan , nous révélons :
⚠️ Les limites pratiques et légales d’un blocage total des visas
💰 La face cachée du système : corruption, business des rendez-vous et rejet massif des demandes
📜 Pourquoi les accords de 1968 sont le vrai objectif de ces manœuvres politiques
Découvrez une analyse approfondie des enjeux réels derrière ces déclarations choc et pourquoi cette menace pourrait bien n’être qu’une posture politique.
📌 Ne ratez pas cette vidéo qui dévoile les dessous d’un sujet sensible et explosif !
👍 Abonnez-vous pour ne rien manquer de nos décryptages sur les relations internationales, les visas et les questions d’immigration.
🔔 Découvrez également notre chaîne secondaire, @CNMPLUS , pour des sujets encore plus audacieux et exclusifs !
#canalnewman

title: Die Familie Mack wünscht frohe Weihnachten!
description:
Unfassbar, was 2024 alles geschehen ist – ein Meilenstein jagte den nächsten. Das vergangene Jahr war das erfolgreichste der Unternehmensgeschichte. Doch auch 2025 verspricht Großes: das 50-jährige Jubiläum des Europa-Park! Freut euch auf unvergessliche Events und zahlreiche Überraschungen. 
Die Familie Mack wünscht euch und euren Familien schöne Weihnachten und ein frohes neues Jahr 2025!

description:
#深圳福田區二百元的海鮮自助餐 #深鲜5D概念海鲜烤肉自助餐廳 #buffet #跟住抖音去搵食系列 #皇庭廣場 #抵食自助餐 #深圳好去處 #深圳美食 #深圳自助餐 #福田 #深圳 #自助餐推介 #福田口岸 #連城新天地 #利奧

深圳福田區二百元的海鮮自助餐｜深鲜·5D概念海鲜烤肉自助餐廳｜跟住抖音去搵食系列｜皇庭廣場｜抵食自助餐｜buffet｜深圳好去處｜深圳美食｜深圳自助餐｜福田｜深圳｜自助餐推介｜福田口岸｜連城新天地｜利奧

在抖會上面，不時會看到一些餐廳廣告
係拍得超吸引
想做一個系列
就是跟住抖音去搵食
親身去幫襯，探店這些在抖音裡
鋪天蓋地賣廣告的餐廳，是否真係咁正
在出發前幾多點讚和訂閱我的頻道
最重要出外影片分享出去


今次要去探店，就是位於福田區
皇廷廣場裏的
深鲜·5D概念海鲜烤肉自助餐
裏面的蒸海鮮，與韓式烤肉真係超吸引
可以搭地鐵去到會展中心站C出口
皇廷廣場出口
出到廣場落一層就會去到我們今日要探店點的餐廳
餐廳開下晝5點30分
我們五點十五分左右已經到達餐廳門口
隔離就是肥滔香港大飯店
其實這一層集中好多餐廳食肆
我們準時入場
大眾點評優惠券就每位218
入場之前，每位畀一百蚊按金，換手上的手環
雖有嘟個手環才可以入場
食完離場之後，退返手環，就會退返100蚊按金

用餐時限120分鐘
地址：福田街道福安社區福華三路118號皇庭廣場G-12號（肥韜茶餐廳隔壁）

title: 🔴 Live in 4K:   XL Wave Forecast = Big Wave Surfing at Historic Waimea Bay, North Shore of Oahu
description:
On Tuesday, December 17, 2024, Waimea Bay on Oahu's North Shore is expected to come alive with a massive swell, bringing waves of breathtaking size and power. This iconic location, renowned for its beauty and legendary surf breaks, will be the perfect vantage point to witness nature's raw energy in action.

As towering waves roll in, surfers and ocean enthusiasts alike will gather to marvel at the spectacle of these awe-inspiring conditions. Whether you're tuning in from afar or lucky enough to be there in person, the scene promises to be nothing short of spectacular.

Prepare to be captivated by the majestic power of Waimea Bay as it showcases some of the most dramatic surf conditions of the season. Don’t miss this incredible opportunity to experience the North Shore at its finest.

Safety Advisory: Due to the anticipated hazardous conditions, it's crucial for spectators to maintain a safe distance from the shoreline and adhere to all local advisories. For the latest updates and detailed information, please refer to the National Weather Service.

Join us for a live stream of this extraordinary big wave surfing event at Waimea Bay, showcasing the prowess and bravery of surfers as they tackle some of the most formidable waves on the planet.

You can experience this exact view in person by staying at these North Shore Waimea Bay oceanfront vacation rentals: https://northshoreoahuvacationrentals.com/ Rent the Oceanfront home: https://northshoreoahuvacationrentals.com/shoreline-house or the Cottage: https://northshoreoahuvacationrentals.com/garden-cottage or the entire property: https://northshoreoahuvacationrentals.com/entire-property.  Mention you're an AfarTV subscriber and receive a 10% discount on your stay!

This view overlooks the mouth of iconic Waimea Bay, the site of the famous big wave surfing competition: the Eddie Aikau. The period spanning from November to February stands out as the optimal window for witnessing large waves. During these months, the waves can reach staggering heights, occasionally exceeding thirty feet, posing a significant risk even for seasoned surfers. It's crucial to always pay attention to warning signs. In contrast, from May to September, the waves mellow out, cultivating a more serene environment suitable for surfing and swimming.  Visible from this camera is The Waiʻanae mountain range on the west side, which separates Central Oʻahu from the Leeward Coast and is the oldest part of Oʻahu at roughly four million years old.   The tallest point of Oahu is Mt Ka'ala at 4,025 feet (1,227 meters). In the evening this camera captures the beautiful sunsets off Ka'ena Point, the westernmost tip of Oahu.


Some information from Wikipedia.

NOTE: 3D audio sound was recorded on site a few days ago. It is not live sound.

(19 Aralık 2024)

Hudutsuz Sevda Perşembe 20.00'de NOW'da!

Nesim’in trajik ölümü, tüm dengeleri altüst ederken Halil İbrahim ve Fikret, intikam için harekete geçer. Zeynep, Halil İbrahim’le tehlikeli bir buluşma gerçekleştirirken, Didem’in bebeğiyle ilgili riskli durumu aileyi daha da zor bir sürece sürükler. Bu sırada İskender ve Kaan’ın hamleleri, yeni bir çatışmanın fitilini ateşler.

Halil İbrahim ve Fikret, Nesim’in intikamını alabilecek mi? Zeynep ve Halil İbrahim arasındaki bağ bu tehlikelerden sağ çıkacak mı?

Küçük bir çocukken kan davası nedeniyle babasını kaybedip İstanbul’a sürülen Halil İbrahim, (Deniz Can Aktaş), 20 yıl sonra memleketi Karadeniz’e yakışıklı, güçlü bir delikanlı olarak geri döner. Burada sevdiği kız Yasemin ile evlenecek ve yeni hayatını kuracaktır. Fakat yaşananlar buna izin vermez. Bir intikam yolculuğuna çıkan Halil İbrahim’in hayatı Leto’lardan Zeynep’in (Miray Daner) çıkması ile tamamen değişecektir.

Desires drive humans, but when those desires become too overwhelming and they grow accustomed to luxury, they lose sensitivity and follow a path that leads to destruction. 
Anmol is a beautiful, brave young woman who works as a teacher and lives with her father and sister. Anmol shares a mutual affection with her cousin Sarim.

title: อร่อยทำง่าย ได้รสชาติแบบต้นฉบับ! “ซุปมันฝรั่งกับต้นกระเทียม” by เชฟพฤกษ์ Wok From Home EP.127
description:
“ซุปมันฝรั่งกับต้นกระเทียม” เมนูอร่อยสุดคลาสสิก ที่เชฟพฤกษ์รับประกันความอร่อย ทั้งจากมันฝรั่งและต้นกระเทียมที่เคี่ยวจนได้รสเข้มข้น และสัมผัสเนียนนุ่ม หอมมัน จากครีมคุณภาพดี กับวิธีการทำที่ไม่ยาก แต่ได้รสชาติสไตล์ฝรั่งเศสแท้ ๆ!

ส่วนผสมสำหรับทำ ซุป
- ครีม Arla Whip & Cook 500 มิลลิลิตร
- ต้นกระเทียมญี่ปุ่น 300 กรัม     
- หอมใหญ่ 300 กรัม
- มันฝรั่ง 500 กรัม         
- เนย 50 กรัม
- น้ำสต๊อก 500 มิลลิลิตร
 
ส่วนผสมสำหรับทำ ขนมปังโรยชีส
- ขนมปัง Baguette 3 ชิ้น
- ชีส 200 กรัม
- น้ำมันมะกอก

ส่วนผสมสำหรับทำ ครีมพลาสลีย์
- ครีม Arla Whip & Cook 150 มิลลิลิตร
- พาสลีย์ 20 กรัม          
- เกลือ สำหรับปรุง
- พริกไทย สำหรับปรุง

วิธีทำ
1.นำเนยมาละลายในหม้อ จากนั้นใส่หัวหอม ต้นกระเทียม และเกลือเล็กน้อย ผัดส่วนผสมด้วยไฟอ่อนจนเริ่มนิ่ม
2.เติมมันฝรั่งลงไปผัดต่อจนเริ่มสลด แล้วจึงเติมน้ำสต๊อกลงไป เร่งไฟรอจนเดือด จากนั้นเปลี่ยนกลับเป็นไฟอ่อน แล้วปิดฝาเคี่ยวต่อเป็นเวลา 10-15 นาที หรือจนกว่ามันฝรั่งจะนิ่ม
3.เติมครีมลงไปเคี่ยว จากนั้นนำไปปั่นจนเนื้อเนียนละเอียด ปิดท้ายด้วยการปรุงรสด้วยเกลือ และพริกไทย
4.ทำขนมปังโรยชีสโดยนำขนมปัง Baguette มาย่างบนกระทะที่ทาบาง ๆ ด้วยน้ำมันมะกอกจนได้สีเหลืองทอง จากนั้นขูดชีสลงบนขนมปัง
5.ทำครีมพาสลีย์เพื่อตกแต่งด้านบนซุป โดยนำครีมมาตีบนชามน้ำแข็งจนขึ้นยอด จากนั้นปรุงรสด้วยเกลือ พริกไทย และพาสลีย์

ABOUT BROOKLYN NINE-NINE
"Brooklyn Nine-Nine" follows the exploits of hilarious Det. Jake Peralta (Andy Samberg) and his stoically ever-professional captain, Raymond Holt (Andre Braugher), along with their diverse, lovable colleagues as they police the NYPD's 99th Precinct. In this final season of the series, Jake and the squad must try to balance their personal lives and their professional lives over the course of a very difficult year.

Rounding out the ensemble is Sgt. Amy Santiago (Melissa Fumera), who has a passion for organization and a weakness for dork dancing; Lt. Terry Jeffords (Terry Crews), a mountain of a man whose most powerful muscle is his sweetheart; Jake's best friend and human puppy dog, Det. Charles Boyle (Joe Lo Truglio); and the incredibly secretive, tough-as-nails Rosa Diaz (Stephanie Beatriz). Also part of the Nine-Nine are veteran officers Det. Scully (Joel McKinnon Miller) and Det. Hitchcock (Dirk Blocker), whose only skill as police officers is their ability to make a passable pot of coffee.

Created by Emmy Award-winning writer/producers Dan Goor and Michael Schur, "Brooklyn Nine-Nine" won the 2014 Golden Globe Awards for Best Television Series - Comedy or Musical and Best Performance by an Actor in a Television Series - Comedy or Musical (Samberg). title: INCREDIBLE FIND! RARE WOODEN GRAVE MARKERS FOUND IN ROADSIDE CEMETERY! Taylor Cemetery
description:
In this video, Cecil Young and I venture to the Taylor Family Cemetery in Marion County, Georgia, where we discover an incredible surprise—nearly 100-year-old wooden headstones, still intact and remarkably preserved. These rare wooden markers provide a unique glimpse into the past, and it’s an honor to document this site and its rich history.

The Taylor Family Cemetery, also known as the Anderson Cemetery, holds a wealth of history and the memory of generations gone by. Among the markers are names, initials, and stories carved into the heart of pine by Uncle Willie Taylor in the 1930s—a labor of love to preserve his family’s legacy.

Check out my other channel, The Old Byrd Farm, for more history, restoration, and exploration content: https://www.youtube.com/@THEOLDBYRDFARMVLOG.

Thank you for joining me on this journey into history!

title: 20-year sentence for husband of Gisèle Pelicot as 51 men guilty in mass rape trial | BBC News
description:
Judges in the French city of Avignon have sentenced Dominique Pelicot to 20 years in prison for aggravated rape after he drugged and abused his then wife, Gisèle Pelicot, and invited dozens of strangers to rape her.

Dominique stood accused alongside 50 other men. Of the 50 co-defendants found guilty, 46 were found guilty of rape, two guilty of attempted rape, and two guilty of sexual assault.

For almost a decade, Gisèle Pelicot was unknowingly given sedatives by her ex-husband, who has admitted to raping her and inviting men he had recruited online to have sex with her in her bed at home while she was unconscious and unaware.

Although Dominique Pelicot admitted the charges against him, most of the other men on trial denied what they did was rape.

It was Gisèle's decision to waive her anonymity and throw this trial into the open - in her words, making "shame swap sides" from the victim to the rapist - something which has turned the 72-year-old into a feminist icon.

Reeta Chakrabarti presents BBC News at Ten reporting by Andrew Harding in Avignon.

title: Urteil in Avignon: 51 Männer nach Missbrauch an Gisèle Pelicot schuldig | WDR Aktuelle Stunde
description:
Im Vergewaltigungsprozess von Avignon sind heute (19.12.2024) der Haupttäter und 50 weitere Männer schuldig gesprochen worden. Gisèle Pelicot war von ihrem Ex-Mann etwa zehn Jahre lang immer wieder betäubt, vergewaltigt und anderen Männern zur Vergewaltigung angeboten worden. Die Richter sprachen ihren Ex-Mann, den 72-jährigen Dominique Pelicot, der schweren Vergewaltigung schuldig und verurteilten ihn zu 20 Jahren Haft. Neben dem Ex-Mann standen 50 weitere Männer vor Gericht. Das Gericht verurteilte alle von ihnen – die meisten wegen "schwerer Vergewaltigung". 

Die drei erwachsenen Kinder des Paares zeigten sich enttäuscht über die ihrer Ansicht nach "niedrigen" Strafen. Auch ein Frauenverband drückte "Unverständnis" aus. Dominique Pelicot hatte seine Taten von Prozessbeginn an gestanden. Viele der Mitangeklagten erklärten, sie seien überzeugt gewesen, sich an einem Sexspiel eines freizügigen Paares beteiligt zu haben. Es gab sogar den Erklärungsversuch, die Anwesenheit ihres Ehemannes wäre ausreichend gewesen, um die Zustimmung der Frau vorauszusetzen. 

Die Taten kamen ans Licht, als der Ex-Mann von Gisèle Pelicot im September 2020 festgenommen wurde, weil er im Supermarkt Frauen unter den Rock gefilmt hatte. Bei den Ermittlungen wurden die Missbrauchsbilder bei ihm gefunden. Die Ermittler konnten etwa 200 Vergewaltigungen an Gisèle Pelicot nachweisen. 

Pelicot ist durch den Prozess zu einer Heldin der Frauenbewegung in Frankreich und darüber hinaus geworden. "Im Jahr 2024 kann niemand mehr sagen: 'Sie hat nichts gesagt, also war sie einverstanden'", sagte die Staatsanwältin zum Ende des Prozesses.

title: Titanic sub: Search teams race against time to find missing vessel - BBC News
description:
Search teams are racing against time to find a tourist submersible that went missing during a dive to the Titanic's wreck on Sunday.

Five people were onboard when contact with the small sub was lost about an hour and 45 minutes into its dive.

The rescue operation is continuing in the mid-Atlantic but there has been no sign of the vessel so far.

US and Canadian agencies, navies and commercial deep-sea firms are all helping the rescue operation.

title: Wok hei: why do stir-fry dishes taste better with the ‘breath of the wok’?
description:
Subscribe to our YouTube channel for free here: 
https://sc.mp/subscribe-youtube

Wok hei is a term that foodies often use to describe the flavour of a perfect stir-fried dish. The Chinese words, meaning “breath of the wok”, refer to a distinct feature of Cantonese cooking, and being able to whip up wok hei is a benchmark skill many professional chefs strive to acquire. Post reporter Lisa Cam spoke with two chefs in Hong Kong to learn about the sometimes elusive art and science behind wok hei and why it has become so beloved with Cantonese food fans around the world.

title: Abuse is ‘a stab to the heart’: trolls target families of Seoul Halloween stampede victims
description:
Subscribe to our YouTube channel for free here: 
https://sc.mp/subscribe-youtube

Lee Jong-chul and Cho Mi-eun lost their son in a deadly crowd crush in South Korea’s capital Seoul on October 29, 2022. But amid their grief, the couple also face a torrent of online abuse that started when they joined a group calling for an investigation into why government officials failed to prevent the deadly Halloween incident. Right-wing trolls who reportedly interpret such efforts as an attack on the government have lashed out at the family with hundreds of negative comments. Some of the online abuse falsely accuses the victims’ families of being profiteers trying to seek compensation.

title: France, EU leaders urge China to 'bring Russia to its senses' | DW News
description:
French President Emmanuel Macron and European Commission President Ursula von der Leyen are in Beijing today for talks with Chinese leader Xi Jinping. After the meeting, the commission president praised the Chinese leader's stance on nuclear weapons, but warned Beijing against arming Russia, claiming that would violate international law. Von der Leyen said that President Xi had stated during talks that he was willing to talk with Ukraine's President Zelenskyy, when the time was right. And she emphasized China's importance in promoting a just peace.

Earlier, Presidents Macron and Xi issued a joint call for peace talks between Russia and Ukraine to take place "as soon as possible." France sees China as a key player in finding a peaceful solution to the war. 

We are talking about this with our Russia correspondent Gzhegosh Shimanovski, who's reporting from the Latvian capital, Riga, since Russia shut down DW's Moscow bureau. Brussels Correspondent Jack Parrock is with us as well.

And we speak with Noah Barkin, China Analyst at the German Marshall Fund think tank.

title: Ree Drummond Makes Sigrid's 5-Star Carrot Cake | The Pioneer Woman | Food Network
description:
When it comes to crowd-pleasing cakes, old-fashioned carrot cake is always at the top of the list. Ree promises this is one of the best carrot cakes she has ever had, with layers of spiced cake, rich cream cheese frosting and pecans!
#ReeDrummond #ThePioneerWoman #FoodNetwork #CarrotCake
Watch #ThePioneerWoman, Saturdays at 10a|9c and #StreamOnMax: https://foodtv.com/StreamOnMaxYT!
Get the recipe ▶ https://foodtv.com/3ZDhs10
Subscribe to Food Network ▶ http://foodtv.com/YouTube

Take one sassy former city girl, her hunky rancher husband, a band of adorable kids, an extended family, cowboys, 3,000 wild mustangs, a herd of cattle and one placid basset hound and you have The Pioneer Woman. The Pioneer Woman is an open invitation into Ree Drummond's life: The award-winning blogger and best-selling cookbook author comes to Food Network and shares her special brand of home cooking, from throw-together suppers to elegant celebrations. The series, set against the incredible story of life at home on the range, is the next best thing to actually sitting on a stool in Ree's kitchen.

Welcome to Food Network, where learning to cook is as simple as clicking play! Grab your apron and get ready to get cookin' with some of the best chefs around the world. We'll give you a behind-the-scenes look at our best shows, take you inside our favorite restaurant and be your resource in the kitchen to make sure every meal is a 10/10!
 
Sigrid's Carrot Cake
Recipe courtesy of Ree Drummond
Level: Easy
Total: 1 hr 40 min
Prep: 20 min
Inactive: 30 min
Cook: 50 min
Yield: 12 servings

Ingredients

Cake:
2 cups granulated sugar
1 cup vegetable oil
4 whole eggs
2 cups all-purpose flour, plus more for dusting
1 teaspoon baking powder
1 teaspoon baking soda
1 teaspoon ground cinnamon
1/2 teaspoon salt
2 cups grated carrots
Butter, for greasing

Icing:
1 stick butter, softened
1 package (8 ounces) cream cheese, softened
1 pound powdered sugar
2 teaspoons vanilla extract
1 cup pecans, chopped finely

Directions

For the cake: Preheat the oven to 350 degrees F. Mix together the granulated sugar, oil and eggs in a large bowl. In another bowl, sift together the flour, baking powder, baking soda, cinnamon and salt. Add the flour mixture to the sugar mixture and combine. Then add the carrots and mix well. Pour the batter into a greased and floured Bundt pan and bake until done, about 50 minutes. Leave to cool completely.

Meanwhile, for the icing: In a larger bowl, cream the butter and cream cheese together. Add the powdered sugar and vanilla and blend. Then mix in the pecans. Spread the icing on the cooled carrot cake.

Eat. Faint. Repeat as needed.

I’ve been fortunate to share my bold baking style with millions of fans on television and online: Netflix’s “Nailed It!”, Food Network’s “Best Baker in America”, "Baker's Dozen" on Hulu, and segments produced for "The Today Show".

This channel, my website, and my two cookbooks all build on my career as a professional chef, which has seen me work in every kind of baking setting you can imagine – from a rundown Tuscan villa, to an Irish priory, to a Michelin-starred restaurant. I’ve had to become creative, imaginative, and bold…and that’s what I want to bring to every one of my “Bold Bakers"!

Visit my website at https://www.BiggerBolderBaking.com for all written recipes including measurements and ingredients.
For brand partner or media opportunities, please contact me at: gemma@biggerbolderbaking.com

#bakingbasics #kitchenhacks #whippedcream

title: LE BOEUF LOC LAC -- FOOD IS LOVE
description:
Découvrez ou redécouvrez la recette du boeuf loc lac, un grand classique de la gastronomie d'une partie de l'Asie du sud est (Cambodge, Laos, Thailande et Vietnam) . De tendres morceaux de boeuf marinés et sautés, accompagnés par du riz sauté à la tomate.
Devenu populaire en France grâce à la restauration, vous allez pouvoir préparer ce festin vous même car ce plat est aussi bon que simple à préparer à conditions de respecter quelques consignes. 
Bon appétit, et n'oubliez pas de vous abonner, et d'activer la cloche 🔔 pour ne rater aucune recette !

300gr de boeuf (filet, rumsteak, biftek, entrecote...)

1 CAS de sauce soja foncée
1 CAS de nuoc mam 
1 CAC d'huile de sésame
1 CAS d'huile de tournesol
1 CAC de fécule de maïs (maïzena)
1/4 de poivre noir moulu
1 CAC de sucre en poudre ( à ajouter en fin de cuisson)

Le riz tomate : 
600gr de riz parfumé cuit
1 CAS d'huile de tournesol
1 ou 2 gousses d'ail
1 CAS de tomate concentrée
1 CAS de ketchup
sel, poivre

La sauce :
2 citrons vert
1 gousse d'ail râpée
1/2 CAC de sel
1/4 ou 1/2 CAC de poivre

title: Which are the Three Functions in Trigonometry? || Grade 10 Mathematics || #InfinityLearn
description:
In the Introduction to Trigonometry chapter for Grade 10, you'll learn about the three primary trigonometric functions that are essential for understanding right triangles: sine, cosine, and tangent. These functions are defined based on the ratios of the sides of a right triangle:

    Sine (sin⁡sin): This function represents the ratio of the length of the side opposite the angle to the length of the hypotenuse. It helps determine vertical heights in various applications.

    Cosine (cos⁡cos): This function represents the ratio of the length of the adjacent side to the length of the hypotenuse. It is useful for finding horizontal distances and is fundamental in many geometric applications.

    Tangent (tan⁡tan): This function is the ratio of the sine to the cosine, or equivalently, the ratio of the opposite side to the adjacent side. It is particularly useful in slope calculations and in situations involving angles of elevation and depression.

Mastering these three functions is crucial for solving problems in trigonometry, as they provide the foundation for understanding more complex relationships in geometry and beyond. Join us as we explore these functions and their applications in detail!

title: Velocity || Motion - Grade 9 Physics || #InfinityLearn
description:
In Grade 9 Physics, velocity is defined as the rate at which an object changes its position.
Key Concepts:

    Definition: Velocity is a vector quantity, meaning it includes both magnitude (speed) and direction. For example, saying "30 m/s to the east" provides a complete description of velocity.

    Calculation: Velocity is calculated by dividing the change in position (displacement) by the time taken for that change.

    Difference from Speed: While speed measures how fast an object is moving regardless of direction, velocity specifies how fast and in which direction the object is moving.

Understanding velocity is essential for analyzing motion and predicting how objects will move in different scenarios, forming a foundational concept in kinematics.


We hope you enjoyed our video!

If you did, please show your support by liking and sharing it. Don’t forget to subscribe to our channel for more exciting content! Thank you!

In the Grade 9 Physics course on motion, students will explore the fundamental concepts that govern how objects move. This comprehensive chapter covers essential topics, including:

    Types of Motion: Discover the various forms of motion, such as linear (straight-line) motion, circular motion, and oscillatory motion.

    Speed and Velocity: Understand the distinction between speed (a scalar quantity) and velocity (a vector quantity), along with the methods for calculating both using distance and time.

    Acceleration: Learn about acceleration as the rate of change of velocity, including the concepts of positive acceleration and negative acceleration (deceleration).

    Graphs of Motion: Gain skills in interpreting and creating motion graphs, such as distance-time and velocity-time graphs, to visualize how an object's position and velocity change over time.

    Equations of Motion: Familiarize yourself with key equations that connect distance, speed, velocity, acceleration, and time, enabling you to solve a variety of motion-related problems.

By the end of this chapter, you will have a thorough understanding of motion, eliminating the need for additional references on this topic. Join us as we delve into the fascinating world of motion!

title: Mount St. Helens Rumbling as Eruptions Predicted 3 Days Ahead
description:
Mount St. Helens is waking up! Since February, hundreds of small earthquakes have been shaking the ground beneath this iconic Washington State volcano, capturing the attention of geologists and volcanologists worldwide. What’s causing this sudden surge in seismic activity? Is the volcano gearing up for another explosive event like its infamous 1980 eruption? In a race against time, scientists have made a groundbreaking discovery: a revolutionary technique that could predict a potential eruption up to three days in advance. But will this be enough to outsmart one of nature's most unpredictable forces? Could we be on the brink of witnessing another geological disaster? The answers might come sooner than we think.

title: Конец амбициям. Смогут ли арабы построить небоскреб за триллион долларов
description:
Планы по строительству футуристического города-стены протяженностью 170 км среди пустыни в Саудовской Аравии меняются на ходу. Будет ли реализован мегапроект за триллионы долларов? 

В 2017 году наследный принц Саудовской Аравии Мухаммед бин Салман представил один из самых амбициозных строительных проектов мира – вертикальный город Зе Лайн. Концепция предполагала возведение сплошного сооружения протяженностью 170 км, высотой 500 метров и шириной всего 200 метров.

Объявленная стоимость проекта составляет 500 млрд долл., но банкиры и аналитики говорят, что расходы будут намного выше. Источники, близкие к проекту, сообщают, что только первые 2,5 километра газопровода будут стоить более 100 миллиардов долларов, а общие расходы, вероятно, превысят 2 триллиона долларов, что превышает ВВП Бразилии

Чтобы помочь воплотить все это в жизнь, власти Саудовской Аравии ввели в эксплуатацию новый бетонный завод стоимостью 190 миллионов долларов США, который сможет производить до 20 000 кубических метров бетона в день, большая часть которого пойдет на линию, а остальная часть — на другие проекты Neom. Кроме того, более 100 000 рабочих заняты вывозом огромных объемов земли 24 часа в сутки, семь дней в неделю, чтобы освободить место для его массивных фундаментов.

Работа над фундаментными сваями также продолжается, из более чем 30 000 свай, установленных на данный момент, около 1 000. Кроме того, проект в настоящее время использует одну пятую всей стали, производимой в мире, что является невероятной статистикой

Однако в 2024 году в западных медиа появилась информация, что проект сделают менее масштабным: длина здания сократится в 70 раз, а количество жителей – в 30 раз. Что пошло не так ли?

Кроме Зе Лайн, в Нэом планируется построить промышленный район, инфраструктуру для зимних видов спорта, морской курорт на острове, развлекательный центр и отели. Финальный объем инвестиций в развитие Нэом не известен, однако, по расчетам аналитиков, сумма составит не менее 2 трлн.

Саудовская Аравия планировала завершить часть работ к 2030 году и заселить туда 1-1,5 млн человек. Саудиты начали строительство в 2023 году. На спутниковых снимках Google за 2024 год видно, что на прямом участке протяженностью более 150 км продолжаются земляные работы, к которым привлечены сотни единиц техники. В  феврале 2024 года Neom опубликовала видео-аэрооблет работ, назвав это величайшей подобной операцией в истории.

Однако весной распространились слухи о прекращении масштабных работ и локализации строительства на меньшем участе. Причина сокращения проекта – дефицит денежных средств. Вместо запланированных 500 млрд долл. у строителей есть только 15-20 млрд долл. Снижение цен на нефть существенно сократило отчисления в суверенный фонд Саудовской Аравии. Более того, Фонд государственных инвестиций еще не утвердил бюджет Neom на 2024 год. По последним данным, протяженность Зе Лайн сократится со 170 км до 2,4 км, высота и ширина не изменятся. В городе такого размера смогут работать и отдыхать 300 тыс. человек.

After years of false starts, a team of computer scientists has found a way to efficiently deduce the Hamiltonian of a quantum system at any constant temperature.

title: Des chercheurs viennent de découvrir une GIGANTIQUE STRUCTURE SOUS L'ANTARCTIQUE...
description:
Il y a un gigantesque secret caché sous la glace de l’Antarctique ! 🧊🌍 Des chercheurs ont découvert une mystérieuse structure plus grande que la Belgique entière et qui pourrait révolutionner notre compréhension de l'histoire de la Terre. Un paysage pétrifié, parfaitement préservé, montre à quoi ressemblait l'Antarctique il y a des millions d'années : un paradis vert rempli de rivières et de forêts. Mais comment un tel paysage peut-il rester inexploré pendant des millions d’années ? Et qu’est-ce que cela signifie pour l’avenir de notre planète ? Grâce à une technologie radar de pointe, les scientifiques ont cartographié un ancien système fluvial qui ressemble à une capsule temporelle. Cette découverte soulève non seulement de nouvelles questions sur le passé, mais montre également comment notre climat pourrait changer à l'avenir. Des lacs sous-glaciaires aux analogies avec la vie extraterrestre sur les lunes glacées, la glace éternelle de l'Antarctique recèle des secrets qui s'étendent bien au-delà de la Terre.

title: THIS Western Weapons Bring Russian Tanks to Their Knees
description:
Tanks and armored vehicles are still indispensable to conquer a territory. Without infantry and tanks advancing, you have no chance of defeating the enemy.
In this situation, destroying or capturing enemy tanks is critical. 
The nearly 3-year battlefield in Ukraine has seen thousands of tanks and armored vehicles fall to their graves. 
When we look at the results, we see huge losses of armored vehicles and tanks, especially in the Russian army.
According to Oryx, which provides independent data analysis, the Russian army has disabled 3625 tanks, 19490 artillery systems and 11255 armored vehicles.
While the data of the Ukrainian Ministry of Defense draws a similar picture in terms of armored vehicles and artillery losses, it claims that Russian tank losses are over 9500. 
Tank and armored vehicle losses are very striking here. 
So how did the Russian army suffer so many tank losses?
Which weapon systems dealt the most devastating blow to Putin's tank army in Ukraine's success?
There is no doubt that the battlefield in Ukraine has brought many innovations to modern warfare. New guerrilla tactics, the rise of drones and the use of multiple rocket launcher systems have gained a critical place in warfare.
These have all taken center stage in the theater of war. But while the use of drones and missiles was very effective and spectacular, it did not have the full potential to stop the enemy invasion. Because their effective performance against tanks and armored vehicles was limited. 
Yes, Ukrainian military drones and artificial intelligence programs were effective in this regard.
However, Ukrainian drones were able to destroy only 10 to 15 percent of Russian tanks and armored vehicles. 
And the remaining losses...
The answer lies in anti-tank missiles. Modern anti-tank missiles are 10 times more powerful than drones in destroying tanks.

현재 지저스웨이브 대표

[ JESUS WAVE ]
■ 소개 
지저스웨이브는 북한의 해방과 구원, 선교하는 통일한국의 비전을 꿈꾸며 기도하는 단체입니다. 또한 나라와 민족, 열방을 향한 주님의 마음을 시원케 하기 위해 기도하는 하나의 운동이며, 흐름입니다. 

저희는 예수의 파도가 한국과 전세계 한민족 교회를 깨우고 북한 우상의 진을 평화적으로 무너뜨릴 수 있기를 기도하고 있습니다. 또한 살려낸 자들이 또 다른 영혼을 살리기 위해, 만주와 연해주를 넘어 땅 끝까지 뻗어갈 그 날이 오기를 기도합니다. 

민족을 깨우고 북한을 재건할 파수꾼들이 더 많이 일어날 수 있도록, 새벽이슬 같은 주의 청년들이 더 많이 세워질 수 있도록 동역을 부탁드립니다. 감사합니다. 

■ 활동 
지저스웨이브는 나라와 민족과 열방을 위한 기도하기 위해 2020년 한국에서 만들어졌습니다.  지저스웨이브는 김성욱 대표의 유튜브채널 외에도, 코로나 팬데믹 이전에는 한국에서 정기적 집회를 진행해왔습니다. 팬데믹 이후에는 온라인 상에서 청년아카데미 및 매일 성경학교 기도회를 운영하고 있습니다. 현재는 온라인을 베이스로 한 청년아카데미와 성경학교 기도회 외에도 한국에서 여름과 겨울 오프라인 성회를 열고 있습니다. 

2023년 7월부터는 미주 시애틀과 LA 등지에서 정기적인 오프라인 집회를 통해 기도하고 있습니다.

title: How AI could steal your digital likeness | Arun Sundararajan | TEDxGateway
description:
Artificial intelligence is generating excitement, but as generative AI mimics the creative processes of individuals, what will happen to human creativity and intelligence? Arun Sundararajan emphasises the importance of humans claiming ownership over their intellectual capital. He explains why traditional intellectual property law falls short and proposes a balance between law and technology for harmonious coexistence between humans and AI. 

Arun Sundararajan is the Harold Price Professor of Entrepreneurship and Technology at New York University, and author of the  best-selling and award-winning book “The Sharing Economy.” He is one of the world's experts on how digital technologies and artificial intelligence transforms business, government and civil society.  He has given hundreds of keynotes including at the World Economic Forum in Davos, and his expert testimony has been sought by the US Congress, the European Parliament, the United Nations, companies, nonprofits and investors globally. 

This talk was given at a TEDx event using the TED conference format but independently organized by a local community. Learn more at https://www.ted.com/tedx

title: 【我想聽更好】第二集『使用效益確認與實用指南』 by 聽力公主的全方位聽力把關課 第2彈
description:
✏️七大主題的全方位聽力攻略課 - 聽力行動👉
https://hearingaction.com/services-video

#聽力行動 #聽力公主 #社會企業
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ep2｜使用效益確認與實用指南

【課程簡介】
有時候，您是否覺得助聽科技的聲音不夠清晰？有購買助聽器的你，明明有助聽專家協助把關，卻還是覺得不夠好，或是你是自行購買輔聽器，沒有助聽專家協助你成效把關。而本課程都會帶你評估輔聽科技為你帶來的成效，建立系統性的效益確認流程，可以讓您的配戴體驗更上一層樓。

【課程目標】
- 介紹日常觀察配戴狀況的五大面向
- 了解常見問題及錦囊妙計
- 介紹年會員專屬聽能導航

【課程適合對象】
- 有使用助聽科技的人
- 不知道自己聽得好不好
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

針對您或家人的聽力狀況，給予專業中立的分析建議
►► 填問卷領 $100折扣卷 | 我對輔聽器、助聽器有興趣 
https://hearact.pse.is/5lr9p2
►► 線上聽力師一對一諮詢
https://hearact.pse.is/5lr9uv 
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

【講師介紹】
哈囉！我是聽力公主 Grace趙藙婷，
一位旅外多年的聽力學家、聽力數位醫療趨勢專家

專長
聽力學、臨床聽力學、嬰幼兒聽力學、助聽器、人工耳蝸、骨導植入式助聽科技、聽力專業教學（耳鼻喉科醫生、聽力師、聽力學碩學士、聽力技術員）、聽力保健講座


學歷
Johns Hopkins University, Fellows Program in Aging, Hearing and Public Health
中山醫學大學 語言治療與聽力學系 學士
台灣國考聽力師

經歷
聽力公主。Hearing Action 聽力YouTube
聽力行動社會企業創辦人
國際危險分貝台灣代表
新加坡國立大學附設醫院聽力學家
新加坡國立大學碩士聽力學系的客座講師與實習指導老師
新加坡全國耳鼻喉科住院醫師年度進修講師(臨床嬰幼兒聽力學課程)
2020 唯一受邀參加WHO西太平洋聽力與耳朵健康會議的台灣人
多家科技公司聽力顧問

我的聽力師生涯在我十幾年的聽力師生涯中，我從第一線看病人、第二線教導學生與專業人士，到飛往不同的國家了解各地的聽力問題。我深深地發現，大眾對於助聽科技有著太多太多的迷思，和錯誤的認知。因此我才決定回到台灣，利用自媒體，提供大家更多正確的觀念，和一般廠家不會告訴你的事情。

我創了一間為聽力困難者的社會企業 #聽力行動，為民眾的聽力需求提供專業的解答，把關民眾購買助聽科技的效益。
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

► 訂閱YoutTube:  @HearingAction  👈

多數社會大眾一定不清楚，聽力也要做復健！但其實佩戴助聽科技就是一個復健的開端，後續的聽能訓練能更幫助找回失去的聽覺能力，而本課程為你介紹聽能復健是什麼、為什麼要做聽能復健、怎麼樣可以透過復健訓練課程聽更好。

title: English Christian Song | "The Despicable Intentions Behind Man’s Belief in God"
description:
Do you want to gain God’s salvation and blessing and escape the empty and boring life? Contact us via WhatsApp: https://shurl.me/ENSPWhatsApp

English Christian Song | "The Despicable Intentions Behind Man’s Belief in God"

God’s deeds are greater in numbers
than the grains of the sands on the beaches,
and His wisdom surpasses all the sons of Solomon,
yet people merely think of Him as a physician of small account,
an unknown teacher of man.
So many only believe in God that He might heal them,
or that He might drive unclean spirits out from their bodies,
and many so that they might receive peace and joy from Him,
and many that they might demand greater wealth from Him.
So many believe in God just to spend this life in peace,
they believe to be safe and sound in the world to come.
Thus, God says that man has faith in Him
because He gives too much grace,
and God says that man has faith in Him
as there’s far too much to gain.

So many just believe in God to avoid the suffering of hell
and receive the blessings of heaven.
So many just believe in Him only for temporary comfort,
yet don’t seek to gain anything in the world that is to come.
Thus, God says that man has faith in Him
because He gives too much grace,
and God says that man has faith in Him
as there’s far too much to gain.

When God brought down His fury upon man,
seized all the joy and peace that he possessed,
man became doubtful.
When God gave to man the suffering of hell
and reclaimed the blessings of heaven,
man’s shame turned to anger.
Thus, God says that man has faith in Him
because He gives too much grace,
and God says that man has faith in Him
as there’s far too much to gain.

When man asked God to heal him,
God loathed him and paid him no heed,
so man left Him to seek the way of evil medicine and sorcery.
When God took everything away,
all that man had demanded from Him,
they disappeared without a trace.
Thus, God says that man has faith in Him
because He gives too much grace,
and God says that man has faith in Him
as there’s far too much to gain.

title: 2023 English Christian Song | "The Holy Spiritual Body of Almighty God Has Appeared" | Choral Hymn
description:
After two thousand years of hoping and waiting, the Lord has finally returned! You're welcome to contact us to learn about the Lord's appearance and work in the last days, and to attend the Lamb's feast.
WhatsApp: https://shurl.me/ENSPWhatsApp

2023 English Christian Song | "The Holy Spiritual Body of Almighty God Has Appeared" | Choral Hymn

Almighty God! In glory He appears.
The holy spirit body, the complete God Himself!
The world is changed, and so too is the flesh.
Transfigured on the mount, He is the person of God.
His clothing pure and white, a crown upon His head,
the world under His feet, and a gold sash around His chest.
His eyes like flames of fire, a sharp sword in His mouth.
And in His right hand seven stars are held.
The kingdom’s path is bright, His glory comes and shines.
The mountains shout for joy, and the water’s laugh replies.
The sun, the moon, and stars follow chosen paths.
They welcome the true God who ends His 6,000-year plan.
Triumphant He returns.
Almighty God! In glory He appears.
The holy spirit body, the complete God Himself!
The world is changed, and so too is the flesh.
Transfigured on the mount, He is the person of God.

The Almighty is on His throne, His chosen dance and praise.
His flag of victory on Mount Zion is raised.
All nations cheer and shout, to God all people sing.
Mount Zion laughs with joy, and God’s glory is appearing.
And even in my dreams, I never thought I’d see,
but I see His face before me now, lay bare my heart to Him.
He gives us food and drink, shines light on life, thoughts and deeds.
And no heart dares oppose, or judgment He will swiftly bring.
And every step He leads.
Almighty God! In glory He appears.
The holy spirit body, the complete God Himself!
The world is changed, and so too is the flesh.
Transfigured on the mount, He is the person of God.

Living, walking, eating, gaining glory, blessings with Him,
together in the kingdom— oh, how sweet, hard to express it.
Face to face conversing, enlightened each and every day.
All mysteries now we see. The holy life’s carefree.
So, run and do not stop; there’s wondrous life ahead.
Don’t settle for a taste, but enter into God instead.
An all-inclusive God, giving all we lack.
We enjoy His words, our life transcendent.
Almighty God! In glory He appears.
The holy spirit body, the complete God Himself!
The world is changed, and so too is the flesh.
Transfigured on the mount,
He is Almighty God, (God gives us all we lack. He encompasses all.)
the complete God Himself! (Cooperate proactively, enjoy the words He speaks.)
The world is changed, and so too is the flesh. (Everything will change. Nothing can disturb us.)
Transfigured on the mount,
He is the person of God. (It is true our life will be transcendent.)

from Follow the Lamb and Sing New Songs

title: 2023 English Christian Song | "Has God's Word Truly Become Your Life?"
description:
After two thousand years of hoping and waiting, the Lord has finally returned! You're welcome to contact us to learn about the Lord's appearance and work in the last days, and to attend the Lamb's feast.
WhatsApp: https://shurl.me/ENSPWhatsApp
Messenger: https://m.me/kingdomsalvationen?ref=youtube

2023 English Christian Song | "Has God's Word Truly Become Your Life?"

Man speaks of letting God be their life,
but they have yet to experience this.
They merely say that God is their life
and that He guides them every day,
that they read His words and pray each day,
and so He has become their life.
Their knowledge is so superficial.
Many people have no foundation;
God’s words have been planted within them,
but have yet to sprout, bear any fruit.
When you’ve experienced to a point,
you couldn’t leave, even if you were made to.
You will always feel you can’t be without having God inside of you.

Being without God is like losing your life.
You’re unable to live without God.
When you’ve experienced to this point,
your faith in God will have hit a mark.
In this way God will become your life and the foundation of your being,
so that you will never again be able to depart from God.
At this point you’ll truly enjoy God’s love,
your bond with God grows even closer,
God will be your life and your love.
This is man’s true stature; it’s real life.

You must experience that God is your life,
such that if God were taken from your heart,
it then would be like losing your life;
God is your life and you can’t leave Him.
This way, you truly experience God.
At this time, when you love God again,
you’ll be able to love God truly.
It will be a singular, pure love.
When experiences have reached a point,
when you pray or eat and drink God’s words,
your heart will be unable to leave God,
you won’t be able to forget Him.

God will have truly become your life.
You can forget the world, and spouses, and kids;
but you’ll have trouble forgetting God.
This is your true life and love for God.
When man’s love for God reaches a point,
nothing compares to their love of God.
Thus they’re able to give up all things
and can accept all of God’s dealings.
When you have been able to achieve
a love of God that surpasses all else,
then you will live in reality,
and you will live in God’s love for you.

from Follow the Lamb and Sing New Songs

title: Rewilding a Suburban Yard
description: I rewild a portion of my yard to support wildlife in the suburbs of Houston.  Managing my emotions regarding, "what the neighbors" think is more difficult than the physical labor to change the landscape. Please read Doug Tallamy's book "Nature's Best Hope", it will change the way you look at turf grass and all the plants you have in your yard. You may be surprised how "ungreen" your yard is, but there are numerous simple actions you can take which will support more robust wildlife in your area. I plan to provide updates to the garden: Episode 2 will include an update on the garden and the installation of the drip irrigation. Episode 3 will be an update on the garden, an inventory of the plants included in the garden and pictures of the creatures which call the garden home.

title: Kung Fury
description: Miami Police Department Detective and martial artist Kung Fury travels in time from the 1980’s to World War II to kill Adolf Hitler (aka "Kung Führer"), and avenge his friend's death at the hands of the Nazi leader. A time machine error sends him further back to the Viking Age. With the help of a female Viking and the Norse God Thor, Kung Fury continues his time travels in order to put an end to the Third Reich once and for all.

title: 奇蹟男孩外傳：白鳥小屋
description: 全球賣座《奇蹟男孩》新篇再掀感動。因欺凌「奇蹟男孩」奧吉而被退學的朱里安（布萊斯基薩　飾）轉校後難以適應新生活。他接待從巴黎而來的外婆（莎拉海倫美蘭　飾）時，得知原來她年輕時也遇過一名「奇蹟男孩」：二戰期間，仍是中學生的莎拉（艾維拉基沙　飾）認識了殘障男同學祖利安（奧蘭度舒韋特　飾），雖然他經常受欺凌，但始終保持善良之心。一日，納粹軍到學校追捕身為猶太人的莎拉，幸得祖利安伸出援手，不但協助她逃跑，還帶她到家裡的小木屋避難。為了保護莎拉，祖利安一家以勇氣、愛與犧牲，對抗無處不在的恐懼...在最黑暗的時刻，一個善良的舉動，成為改變人一生的奇蹟！

title: Venom: The Last Dance
description: In Venom: The Last Dance, Tom Hardy returns as Venom, one of Marvel's greatest and most complex characters, for the final film in the trilogy. Eddie and Venom are on the run. Hunted by both of their worlds and with the net closing in, the duo are forced into a devastating decision that will bring the curtains down on Venom and Eddie's last dance.Venom: The Last Dance stars Tom Hardy, Chiwetel Ejiofor, Juno Temple, Rhys Ifans, Peggy Lu, Alanna Ubach and Stephen Graham. The film is directed by Kelly Marcel from a screenplay she wrote, based on a story by Hardy and Marcel. The film is produced by Avi Arad, Matt Tolmach, Amy Pascal, Kelly Marcel, Tom Hardy and Hutch Parker.
